. Discover now!","name":"Interior Architecture in Turkey 2025: List of Best Universities","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/interior-architecture-in-turkey/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/interior-architecture-in-turkey/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/interior-architecture-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/interior-architecture-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Average Interior Architect Salary in Turkey </h2>



