</figure>
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote">


<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Note:</strong> These scores are estimates based on data from 2024. Updates should be made when the 2025 application guidelines are announced.</p>


</blockquote>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some universities, such as Boğaziçi and METU, offer astrophysics courses within the physics program, not directly in Astronomy. Therefore, it is important to check the department name carefully when applying.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Source: <a href="https://yokatlas.yok.gov.tr/netler.php" data-type="link" data-id="https://yokatlas.yok.gov.tr/netler.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YÖK Atlas Base Points</a></p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="visa-and-scholarship-guide-for-foreign-students">Visa and Scholarship Guide for Foreign Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The visa process for foreign students who want to study Astronomy or Astrophysics in Turkey is quite simple. After you receive your acceptance letter, it is enough to fill out the online application form and make an appointment at the consulate. When you complete the documents such as passport, accommodation information, etc., your visa is usually approved without any problems.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As for scholarships, <strong><a class="" href="https://www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Turkey Scholarships</a></strong> is the most comprehensive state-funded program. They offer housing, health insurance and a monthly allowance. There are also additional opportunities with merit scholarships and project support at universities such as Ege, Istanbul and METU.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you prepare well, it is definitely possible to study Astronomy in Turkey with a scholarship.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="now-is-the-time-to-set-your-eyes-on-the-sky-and-come-to-turkey">Now is the time to set your eyes on the sky and come to Turkey!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Astronomy and Space Sciences is not just a subject; it is a matter of curiosity and passion. And if you want to pursue this passion, Turkey is waiting for you. With its academically strong universities, modern observatories, curricula that provide a transition from theory to practice, and student-friendly cities, it is very possible to find a place for yourself here.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Now is the time to take your dream a little more seriously and take the first step. Maybe you are the next scientist to explore the sky.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2026-02-20T06:26:20Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-02-01T07:03:27Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/astronomy-and-space-science-programs-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Astronomy and Space Science Programs in Turkey","title":"astronomy-and-space-science-programs-in-turkey"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'astronomy-and-space-science-programs-in-turkey';
